   "source": [
    "## 9. Coordonnées factorielles\n",
    "\n",
    "### 9.1 Calcul des coordonnées\n",
    "\n",
    "**Coordonnées des lignes (régions)** sur l'axe k:\n",
    "$$\\Psi_{ik} = \\frac{U_{ik}}{\\sqrt{f_{i.}}}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Coordonnées des colonnes (candidats)** sur l'axe k:\n",
    "$$\\Phi_{jk} = \\frac{V_{jk}}{\\sqrt{f_{.j}}}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "### 9.2 Propriétés des coordonnées\n",
    "\n",
    "- Moyennes pondérées nulles: $\\sum_i f_{i.} \\Psi_{ik} = 0$\n",
    "- Variance = valeur propre: $\\sum_i f_{i.} \\Psi_{ik}^2 = \\lambda_k$\n",
    "- Covariance nulle entre axes: $\\sum_i f_{i.} \\Psi_{ik} \\Psi_{ik'} = 0$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Coordonnées factorielles des lignes (régions)\n",
    "# Ψ_{ik} = U_{ik} / sqrt(f_{i.})\n",
    "psi_raw = U / np.sqrt(f_row[:, np.newaxis])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Coordonnées factorielles des colonnes (candidats)\n",
    "# Φ_{jk} = V_{jk} / sqrt(f_{.j})\n",
    "phi_raw = V / np.sqrt(f_col[np.newaxis, :])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Normaliser par les valeurs singulières pour obtenir les vrais scores\n",
    "psi = psi_raw * singular_values[np.newaxis, :]\n",
    "phi = phi_raw * singular_values[np.newaxis, :]\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"ÉTAPE 7: Coordonnées factorielles\")\n",
    "print(\"=\"*100)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nCoordonnées des LIGNES (Régions):\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 100)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_psi = pd.DataFrame(psi[:, :5],\n",
    "                      index=df_raw.index,\n",
    "                      columns=[f'Dim.{i+1}' for i in range(5)])\n",
    "print(df_psi.round(4))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nCoordonnées des COLONNES (Candidats):\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 100)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_phi = pd.DataFrame(phi[:, :5],\n",
    "                      index=df_raw.columns,\n",
    "                      columns=[f'Dim.{i+1}' for i in range(5)])\n",
    "print(df_phi.round(4))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Vérifier les propriétés\n",
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*100)\n",
    "print(\"Vérification des propriétés des coordonnées:\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 100)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Moyennes pondérées (doivent être ~0)\n",
    "mean_psi_1 = np.sum(f_row * psi[:, 0])\n",
    "mean_phi_1 = np.sum(f_col * phi[:, 0])\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n1. Moyennes pondérées (doivent être ≈ 0):\")\n",
    "print(f\"   Moyenne lignes axe 1: {mean_psi_1:.10f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"   Moyenne colonnes axe 1: {mean_phi_1:.10f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Variances (doivent égaler λ_k)\n",
    "var_psi_1 = np.sum(f_row * psi[:, 0] ** 2)\n",
    "var_phi_1 = np.sum(f_col * phi[:, 0] ** 2)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n2. Variances (doivent égaler λ_k = {eigenvalues[0]:.6f}):\")\n",
    "print(f\"   Variance lignes axe 1: {var_psi_1:.6f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"   Variance colonnes axe 1: {var_phi_1:.6f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Covariance entre axes (doivent être ~0)\n",
    "cov_psi = np.sum(f_row * psi[:, 0] * psi[:, 1])\n",
    "cov_phi = np.sum(f_col * phi[:, 0] * phi[:, 1])\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n3. Covariances entre axes (doivent être ≈ 0):\")\n",
    "print(f\"   Covariance lignes axes 1-2: {cov_psi:.10f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"   Covariance colonnes axes 1-2: {cov_phi:.10f}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
