   "source": [
    "## 10. Contributions et qualités de représentation\n",
    "\n",
    "### 10.1 Contribution à l'inertie de l'axe\n",
    "\n",
    "**Contribution de la ligne i à l'axe k**:\n",
    "$$Ctr(i, F_k) = \\frac{f_{i.} \\times \\Psi_{ik}^2}{\\lambda_k}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Contribution de la colonne j à l'axe k**:\n",
    "$$Ctr(j, F_k) = \\frac{f_{.j} \\times \\Phi_{jk}^2}{\\lambda_k}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "### 10.2 Qualité de représentation (cosinus carré)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Qualité de la ligne i**:\n",
    "$$QLT(i, F_k) = \\frac{\\Psi_{ik}^2}{\\sum_t \\Psi_{it}^2}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Mesure la proportion de l'inertie de i expliquée par l'axe k."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Contributions des lignes aux axes\n",
    "contrib_rows = np.zeros((psi.shape[0], psi.shape[1]))\n",
    "for k in range(psi.shape[1]):\n",
    "    contrib_rows[:, k] = (f_row * psi[:, k] ** 2) / eigenvalues[k]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Contributions des colonnes aux axes\n",
    "contrib_cols = np.zeros((phi.shape[0], phi.shape[1]))\n",
    "for k in range(phi.shape[1]):\n",
    "    contrib_cols[:, k] = (f_col * phi[:, k] ** 2) / eigenvalues[k]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Inertie relative (qualité de représentation) des lignes\n",
    "total_inertia_rows = np.sum(psi ** 2, axis=1)\n",
    "quality_rows = np.zeros((psi.shape[0], psi.shape[1]))\n",
    "for k in range(psi.shape[1]):\n",
    "    quality_rows[:, k] = (psi[:, k] ** 2) / total_inertia_rows\n",
    "\n",
    "# Inertie relative (qualité de représentation) des colonnes\n",
    "total_inertia_cols = np.sum(phi ** 2, axis=1)\n",
    "quality_cols = np.zeros((phi.shape[0], phi.shape[1]))\n",
    "for k in range(phi.shape[1]):\n",
    "    quality_cols[:, k] = (phi[:, k] ** 2) / total_inertia_cols\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"ÉTAPE 8: Contributions et qualités de représentation\")\n",
    "print(\"=\"*100)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nContributions des RÉGIONS aux axes factoriels (%):\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 100)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_contrib_rows = pd.DataFrame(contrib_rows[:, :4] * 100,\n",
    "                               index=df_raw.index,\n",
    "                               columns=[f'Axe {i+1}' for i in range(4)])\n",
    "print(df_contrib_rows.round(2))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nContributions des CANDIDATS aux axes factoriels (%):\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 100)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_contrib_cols = pd.DataFrame(contrib_cols[:, :4] * 100,\n",
    "                               index=df_raw.columns,\n",
    "                               columns=[f'Axe {i+1}' for i in range(4)])\n",
    "print(df_contrib_cols.round(2))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*100)\n",
    "print(\"Qualités de représentation des RÉGIONS (%):\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 100)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_quality_rows = pd.DataFrame(quality_rows[:, :4] * 100,\n",
    "                               index=df_raw.index,\n",\    "columns=[f'Axe {i+1}' for i in range(4)])\n",
    "print(df_quality_rows.round(2))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nQualités de représentation des CANDIDATS (%):\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 100)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_quality_cols = pd.DataFrame(quality_cols[:, :4] * 100,\n",
